    <content>&lt;P&gt;Hello Experts,&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;I am trying to integrate files upload from SAP Build Apps into my process automation approval inbox. To achieve this I have followed below steps.&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;Step1:&amp;nbsp;created a process automation creating input variable type as upload file as shown below :&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="rupeshpandit1999_0-1710334131274.png" style="width: 620px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/79961iAF62D8E3E104285E/image-dimensions/620x241?v=v2" width="620" height="241" role="button" title="rupeshpandit1999_0-1710334131274.png" alt="rupeshpandit1999_0-1710334131274.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="rupeshpandit1999_1-1710334139860.png" style="width: 618px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/79967i6DEF00B441C85695/image-dimensions/618x217?v=v2" width="618" height="217" role="button" title="rupeshpandit1999_1-1710334139860.png" alt="rupeshpandit1999_1-1710334139860.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;Step2 :Created a project in SAP Build Apps for upload document as shown below&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="rupeshpandit1999_2-1710334308010.png" style="width: 619px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/79970iD56C989E58535F5A/image-dimensions/619x338?v=v2" width="619" height="338" role="button" title="rupeshpandit1999_2-1710334308010.png" alt="rupeshpandit1999_2-1710334308010.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;Step3: Map the variables at data level in SAP Build Apps&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="rupeshpandit1999_3-1710334388677.png" style="width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/79971i30F3BA12296074EF/image-size/medium?v=v2&amp;amp;px=400" role="button" title="rupeshpandit1999_3-1710334388677.png" alt="rupeshpandit1999_3-1710334388677.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;When I execute the build apps Form document is upload successfully I am getting toast message as below&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="rupeshpandit1999_4-1710334481687.png" style="width: 538px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/79974i15A8997BE471E679/image-dimensions/538x289?v=v2" width="538" height="289" role="button" title="rupeshpandit1999_4-1710334481687.png" alt="rupeshpandit1999_4-1710334481687.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;But the issue is unloaded document is not coming to inbox of my process automation, Please advice any suggestion to resolve this issue.&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;Thanks,&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;Rupesh&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;</content>
