    <author>
      <name>SM2023</name>
      <uri>https://community.sap.com/t5/user/viewprofilepage/user-id/169649</uri>
    </author>
    <content>&lt;DIV class=""&gt;&lt;DIV class=""&gt;&lt;DIV class=""&gt;&lt;DIV class=""&gt;&lt;DIV class=""&gt;&lt;DIV class=""&gt;&lt;DIV class=""&gt;&lt;P&gt;Hello SAP Build Apps Experts,&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;I've encountered a challenge regarding new entity creation with the introduction of &lt;STRONG&gt;Roles&lt;/STRONG&gt;. Initially, after creating entities, I defined roles and successfully added users. However, when attempting to create a new entity subsequently, it does not appear in the list of entities under "Roles". I've ensured deployment after creating the new entity &lt;SPAN&gt;and even tried re-logging in, just in case &lt;span class="lia-unicode-emoji" title=":confused_face:"&gt;😕&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/SPAN&gt;, yet it remains absent from the list.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;I expect that any new entity created should automatically be available in the list, allowing us to designate actions for specific roles. At the very least, there should be an option to manually add the new entity if it isn't automatically listed.&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;Looking forward to resolving this issue.&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href="https://community.sap.com/t5/c-khhcw49343/SAP+Build+Apps/pd-p/6cfd8176-04ae-4548-8f38-158456e1a47a" class="lia-product-mention" data-product="1176-1"&gt;SAP Build Apps&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;</content>
