    <content>&lt;P&gt;I am creating an application using 'SAP Build Apps', creating a classic data entity.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;When I create the integration thus:&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="Configure ODAT integration" style="width: 853px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/90346i38748A17697F552F/image-size/large?v=v2&amp;amp;px=999" role="button" title="Fig1.png" alt="Configure ODAT integration" /&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-caption" onclick="event.preventDefault();"&gt;Configure ODAT integration&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;and successfully test with these selections:&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="Test" style="width: 852px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/90349i42E19C106E09C327/image-size/large?v=v2&amp;amp;px=999" role="button" title="Fig2.png" alt="Test" /&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-caption" onclick="event.preventDefault();"&gt;Test&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;The Relative Path in the config tab remains unchanged:&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="config" style="width: 858px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/90352i4161007EAD93B06C/image-size/large?v=v2&amp;amp;px=999" role="button" title="Fig3.png" alt="config" /&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-caption" onclick="event.preventDefault();"&gt;config&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;Saving the resource simply defaults to the selection of all fields.&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;I hope I have missed something here and would appreciate some assistance.&lt;/P&gt;</content>
    <link href="https://community.sap.com/t5/technology-q-a/sap-build-apps-configure-odata-integration-selected-fields-not-displayed-in/qaq-p/13657073"/>
