    <content>&lt;P&gt;Hello Experts,&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;We are trying to create external user id using Identity Directory API action project in SAP Build Process Automation with IAS destination. we are executing the creates a user resource action within Automation where we are getting the below error :&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;FONT color="#000000"&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&lt;FONT color="#333333"&gt;The provided destination does not follow the expected &lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;FONT color="#000000"&gt;&lt;FONT color="#333333"&gt;structure&lt;/FONT&gt;.&lt;/FONT&gt; &lt;FONT color="#333333"&gt;Please contact &lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;FONT color="#000000"&gt;&lt;FONT color="#333333"&gt;support&lt;/FONT&gt;.&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="rupeshpandit1999_0-1712558214541.png" style="width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/92638i524D38E0F6E802C1/image-size/medium/is-moderation-mode/true?v=v2&amp;amp;px=400" role="button" title="rupeshpandit1999_0-1712558214541.png" alt="rupeshpandit1999_0-1712558214541.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;Note : when are executing this action directly from connectors out of the automation we are able to create use id successfully.&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;Could you please Help or suggest any solution on this error, how we can resolve it.&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;Thanks,&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;Rupesh&lt;/P&gt;</content>
